<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="del-trans-2020-03-crypt"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Recorded items for month 2020-03</title></titleStmt><publicationStmt><p>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</p></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><p>Created by members of the TLS project</p></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation>Initially created: <date>2020-03-27T23:09:45.553+09:00</date>.</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Items</head><p xml:id="del-2020-03-start"><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T23:09:45.553+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">The Duke did not refuse the gift,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T23:25:08.008+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">you still cause your minister to lose his good fortune</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.60" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-27T23:36:58.461+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">To promote the worthy and to demote the incompetent</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-9a.66" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-28T00:44:55.053+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Bólǐ Xī became the Senior Minister and took control of affairs.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-10a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-28T00:47:12.529+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Zhào Jiǎnzhǔ was going from Jìnyáng to Hándān</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-10a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-28T00:55:09.963+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">He sped on for another one hundred steps, and then he stopped again.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-10a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-28T00:56:12.194+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">The official was about to step forward to remonstrate.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-10a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-28T00:59:25.193+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Dǒng Ānyǔ said;</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-10a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-28T01:01:12.52+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">I have forgotten to order someone to take it along.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-10a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-28T01:09:41.752+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">when I left I forgot to order someone to say farewell to him and to give him presents.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-11a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-28T01:58:21.712+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">The Duke said;</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-11a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-28T02:01:25.611+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">"I am not your cook.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-11a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-28T02:03:45.856+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">The Duke said;</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-11a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-28T02:11:52.063+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">I beg to refuse your request."</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-11a.25" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-28T02:12:04.722+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">he is capalbe of organising the system of all the bureaucratic offices</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-12a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-28T04:17:26.131+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">"One separates off territory to enfeoff him with</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-12a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-28T04:17:46.532+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">can that be called loyal devotion.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-12a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-28T04:19:34.261+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">"If his proposals are followed</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-13a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-29T01:13:14.906+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">but still I am terrified to think that I am luxurious and do to pay enough attention to the implementation of my duties.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-14a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-29T17:59:25.617+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">Yànzǐ replied:</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-14a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-29T18:06:13.985+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">this amounts to hiding away your gifts to him.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-14a.29" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-29T21:15:33.754+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">and you have a plaited carriage</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-14a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-30T02:51:13.572+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">or shall I first give my explanation before I get to drink the penalty beer?</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-14a.35" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-30T02:51:57.258+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">or shall I first give my explanation before I get to drink the penalty beer?"</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-14a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-30T02:57:31.481+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">but I would not presume to accept this for the sake of becoming rich</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-14a.31" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-30T02:58:21.45+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">So this counts as hiding away the ruler's gifts.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-14a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-30T03:01:51.485+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">I am told that worthy ruler in antiquity</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-1a.40" xml:lang="en" resp="CH" modified="2020-03-30T04:58:00.868+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">                                    all having public progress in mind,</seg><seg corresp="#KR6q0003_T_001-0204c.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2020-03-31T16:54:45.746+09:00" resp-del="#chris" src-id="KR6q0003-en">Talking only of this Good Kalpa</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-14a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-31T20:55:51.731+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">when their ministers accepted abundant munificence but did not focus on the state and its ruling family</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-14a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-31T20:56:18.446+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">then he would fault them for that;</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-14a.53" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-31T20:57:35.178+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">are my seniors.</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-14a.67" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-31T21:30:27.807+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">and non of the likes o my mother have insufficient supplies of clothes and food,</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-14a.68" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-31T21:31:00.168+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">and none of the likes of my wife</seg><seg corresp="#CH1a0907_CHANT_002-14a.71" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2020-03-31T22:28:21.739+09:00" resp-del="#CH" src-id="CH1a0907-en">or is it to propagate the ruler's generous gifts.</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>